<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrīśākavarṣē dyubhujaravimitē siṁhamāsē tṛtīyādasra<unclear>r</unclear>kṣē
<lb n="2"/>sōmavārē harakulatilakō gōtrataḥ kāśyapākhyaḥ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> māṁkkādityasya sū
<lb n="3" break="no"/>nu<unclear>r</unclear>vimalatarajaya<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śrījaya<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>takṣamābhṛcchrīdēvīnaṁdanōyaṁ viśada 
<lb n="4" break="no"/>naraharēssiṁhabhūbha<supplied reason="omitted">r</supplied>tṛbharttuḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> paṁcchāśannaicikīnāṁ gaṇa<unclear>ma</unclear>diśadamā dī
<lb n="5" break="no"/>padaṁḍḍaṁ svadīpāvicchityai gōpayuktaṁ savṛṣaparivṛḍhaṁ svīyarājyā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>bhivṛdhyai <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> pūjārtthaṁ puṣpavāṭīṁ bahukusumaphalāmāśaśāṁkkārkka
<lb n="7" break="no"/>tāraṁ dharmmāvētau samṛddhaṁ viśadataradhiyō vaiṣṇavāḥ pālayaṁttu <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied>
<lb n="8"/>śakavarṣaṁbulu 1220 gunēṁṭi siṁha kṛṣṇa tṛtīyyayu sōmavāramunāṁḍu
<lb n="9"/>Oḍḍavādi māṁkādityadēvarājula koḍku jayaṁttikadēvarājulu tama rājyā
<lb n="10" break="no"/>bhivṛddhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sannidhiyaṁdu dīpadaṁḍu sahitamugā<note n="387-1">The inscription stops here.</note>
</p>

